   rc = @{i}Success @{ui} 

@{b}Function: @{ub}  Activates the field with the specified ID in the mask. Only 
   fields, which appear as a string/longint gadget may be activated. If 
   project or window is not active, the field cannot be activated. This 
   command may be only called in mask mode. 

