@node BUGS "Bugs" 

@{b}@{u}Bugs@{ub}@{uu}

If you find some bugs in Fiasco, send a detailed description to @{"me" link author}. 
Please include information about your processor, OS version and other 
configuration. 

@{b}These bugs are currently known:@{ub}


    
@{b}·@{ub}  The frame of the list window flashes sometimes in a weird way 
   under Kickstart 37.x  

@{b}·@{ub}  ARexx seems to have problems with filenames, which contain spaces. The 
   name is only interpreted to the the first space. This affects the full 
   path, because Fiasco expands the name to the full path before calling 
   ARexx scripts.  

@{b}·@{ub}  Seems to leave sometimes some memory allocated.  

@endnode 
@node TODO "To do" 

@{b}@{u}To do@{ub}@{uu}

Fiasco is of course not perfect, at all. Here is a list of all things, 
which will be perhaps added at a later point (no guarantee!). If you have 
an Idea, send it to @{"me" link Author}! 

    
@{b}·@{ub}  Better scrolling in the mask window. I currently use GadTools 
   gadgets, which have to be recreated if you want to change their 
   positions. I plan to emulate the used gadgets. This would not require 
   any more GZZ windows. 

@{b}·@{ub}  New searchfunction. 

@{b}·@{ub}  Sorting should be take several fields into account and should get 
   faster. 

@{b}·@{ub}  New ARexx commands: ReadRecord and WriteRecord. Should read all 
   fieldcontents and put them in ARexx variables with the field id as 
   names. 

@{b}·@{ub}  New searchpatterns. 

@{b}·@{ub}  Hiding of fields in the mask. 

@{b}·@{ub}  Print function; Reports 

@{b}·@{ub}  Stringfields, which support multiple lines 

@{b}·@{ub}  Reversed logic while searching and counting 

@{b}·@{ub}  AppWindows for Datatypes and Extern Fields 

@{b}·@{ub}  "Packing" of projects: search for unused fields and make used as small 
   as possible. 

@{b}·@{ub}  Checking, whether a similar record already exists (automatically) 

@{b}·@{ub}  Ability to specify the order, how the fields are activated after a 
   Return. 

@{b}·@{ub}  Save status of list window. 

@{b}·@{ub}  Fiasco should not have to read the whole file. (To save memory) 

@{b}·@{ub}  Iconify projects 

@{b}·@{ub}  Extend ARexx commands, that they can refer to other records than the 
   current. 

@{b}·@{ub}  Separator bars for Mask 

@{b}·@{ub}  ServiceWindow hides the unused gadgets instead of disabling them 

@{b}·@{ub}  List fieldtype with "Add" and "Del" 

@{b}·@{ub}  "ARexx hook" for extending relations 

@{b}·@{ub}  Better support of mask mode in ARexx 

@endnode 
